{
  "stem": "293.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was making pretty good money because I met Schindler, Oskar Schindler, who later on I found out that he's a very decent human being who was interpreter.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he came to my mother, commanded by a Jew, for my mother redecorate the apartment for the Jewish fellow, and he purchased from the Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He paid him 50,000 zloty, which was quite a big amount of money at this time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe $5,000, $6,000.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This Oskar Schindler came over and was recommended.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother hesitated.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's interesting, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I still have my pistol, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When I was dressing up, there was not the real military revolver.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This I lost over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's buried in the ground in [INAUDIBLE] over there in the hospital someplace.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I dig it in the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "My little one, [INAUDIBLE], you know, when I was dating a girl and I went in the uniform, I put the pistol to impress her a little bit more.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] That's all  what was the fun for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when I saw-- when somebody was knocking on the door-- and I was alone with my mother-- and I-- my mother looked through the look area, you know, in the door, you know, the viewer.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she said, Pol, it's Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "She saw through this door looker a guy with a big swastika, swastika.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he-- she was thinking he's Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I have the pistol put behind my belt.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I figure out probably I have to fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That was stupid thinking.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But this is way you think when you're young.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we still didn't know what kind problems you can have.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I said to her, let him in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I hide behind the door and listen to the conversation.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
